comment:
* Civic Address key types used to define address elements. * *

These keys can be used with {@code ResponderLocation.toCivicLocationSparseArray()} * to look-up the corresponding string values.

variables.name: LANGUAGE
variables.comment: Language key e.g. i-default.

variables.name: STATE
variables.comment: Category label A1 key e.g. California.

variables.name: COUNTY
variables.comment: Category label A2 key e.g. Marin.

variables.name: CITY
variables.comment: Category label A3 key e.g. San Francisco.

variables.name: BOROUGH
variables.comment: Category label A4 key e.g. Westminster.

variables.name: NEIGHBORHOOD
variables.comment: Category label A5 key e.g. Pacific Heights.

variables.name: GROUP_OF_STREETS
variables.comment: Category label A6 key e.g. University District.

variables.name: PRD
variables.comment: Leading Street direction key e.g. N.

variables.name: POD
variables.comment: Trailing street suffix key e.g. SW.

variables.name: STS
variables.comment: Street suffix or Type key e.g Ave, Platz.

variables.name: HNO
variables.comment: House Number key e.g. 123.

variables.name: HNS
variables.comment: House number suffix key e.g. A, 1/2.

variables.name: LMK
variables.comment: Landmark or vanity address key e.g. Golden Gate Bridge.

variables.name: LOC
variables.comment: Additional Location info key e.g. South Wing.

variables.name: NAM
variables.comment: Name of residence key e.g. Joe's Barbershop.

variables.name: POSTAL_CODE
variables.comment: Postal or ZIP code key e.g. 10027-1234.

variables.name: BUILDING
variables.comment: Building key e.g. Lincoln Library.

variables.name: APT
variables.comment: Apartment or suite key e.g. Apt 42.

variables.name: FLOOR
variables.comment: Floor key e.g. 4.

variables.name: ROOM
variables.comment: Room key e.g. 450F.

variables.name: TYPE_OF_PLACE
variables.comment: Type of place key e.g. office.

variables.name: PCN
variables.comment: Postal community name key e.g. Leonia.

variables.name: PO_BOX
variables.comment: Post Office Box key e.g. 12345.

variables.name: ADDITIONAL_CODE
variables.comment: Additional Code key e.g. 13203000003.

variables.name: DESK
variables.comment: Seat, desk, pole, or cubical key e.g. WS 181.

variables.name: PRIMARY_ROAD_NAME
variables.comment: Primary road name key e.g. Shoreline.

variables.name: ROAD_SECTION
variables.comment: Road Section key e.g. 14.

variables.name: BRANCH_ROAD_NAME
variables.comment: Branch Rd Name key e.g. Lane 7.

variables.name: SUBBRANCH_ROAD_NAME
variables.comment: Subbranch Rd Name key e.g. Alley 8.

variables.name: STREET_NAME_PRE_MODIFIER
variables.comment: Premodifier key e.g. Old.

variables.name: STREET_NAME_POST_MODIFIER
variables.comment: Postmodifier key e.g. Service.

variables.name: SCRIPT
variables.comment: Script key e.g. Latn.
